    <section id="section-required" class="app-section">
      <h2 class="hca-typography--title">Required</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <div class="hca-layout__container--body-content">
            <p class="hca-typography--body-1">Fields are required by default, unless noted as optional. First, eliminate as many optional fields as possible. If some fields truly are necessary, but only apply to a subset of users, don’t make users find out through trial and error. Limit the form to only 1 or 2 optional fields, and clearly label them as optional.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-1">
